text: The Iranian Business Council - Dubai is a business council formed by Iranian expatriates in Dubai, United Arab Emirates. The council promotes trade relations between Iran and the United Arab Emirates. ==See also== * Iranian Club, Dubai * Iran–United Arab Emirates relations ==References== ==External links== * * Category:Business organisations based in the United Arab Emirates Category:Iranian diaspora in the United Arab Emirates Category:Iran–United Arab Emirates relations Category:Organisations based in Dubai
